LEE, Respondent, v. PETRIE et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fourth Department. May 18, 1894.) Action by Janette J. Lee, as executrix, etc., against Thomas Petrie and others.

Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JJ.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
